One of the stories that I tell you,

4
00:00:08,109 --> 00:00:10,060
one of the stories will be true,

5
00:00:10,060 --> 00:00:12,140
and the other story will be a lie.

6
00:00:12,140 --> 00:00:14,850
But I'm not going to tell
you which one is which.

7
00:00:14,850 --> 00:00:16,660
You will need to guess.

8
00:00:16,660 --> 00:00:20,440
So listen to both stories and
maybe in the comments below,

9
