16
00:00:38,880 --> 00:00:41,740
Story number one, "The Pet Puppy."

17
00:00:41,740 --> 00:00:43,840
One day when I was about 10 years old,

18
00:00:43,840 --> 00:00:46,150
my parents told me that
we would be getting

19
00:00:46,150 --> 00:00:47,630
a new puppy soon.

20
00:00:47,630 --> 00:00:49,730
Our dog Prince, was getting old

21
00:00:49,730 --> 00:00:52,310
and they thought it would
be good to get a new dog

22
00:00:52,310 --> 00:00:53,920
while Prince was still around,

23
00:00:53,920 --> 00:00:58,100
so that the new puppy could
learn how to behave from him.

24
00:00:58,100 --> 00:01:00,080
My sister begged them to get a poodle,

25
00:01:00,080 --> 00:01:03,120
but my parents said that
wouldn't be a good breed of dog

26
00:01:03,120 --> 00:01:04,200
for a farm.

27
00:01:04,200 --> 00:01:06,370
And that we'd be getting
a dog from the neighbors,

28
00:01:06,370 --> 00:01:09,230
because it was free and both its parents

29
00:01:09,230 --> 00:01:11,230
were good farm dogs.

30
00:01:11,230 --> 00:01:13,260
My sister and I were really excited.

31
00:01:13,260 --> 00:01:15,610
And we got a special
place ready in the barn

32
00:01:15,610 --> 00:01:17,080
for the new puppy.

33
00:01:17,080 --> 00:01:19,370
We put some straw in a big cardboard box

34
00:01:19,370 --> 00:01:21,600
and got a couple old
bowls from the kitchen

35
00:01:21,600 --> 00:01:23,240
for water and food.

36
00:01:23,240 --> 00:01:26,010
We even got to go to the
pet store with our mom,

37
00:01:26,010 --> 00:01:28,440
to buy a bag of puppy chow.

38
00:01:28,440 --> 00:01:29,320
A couple of days later,

39
00:01:29,320 --> 00:01:32,580
we went to the neighbor's
farm to pick out our puppy.

40
00:01:32,580 --> 00:01:35,520
Their dog had, had a litter of seven pups

41
00:01:35,520 --> 00:01:37,670
and we would have first choice.

42
00:01:37,670 --> 00:01:39,240
We were excited.

43
00:01:39,240 --> 00:01:43,490
The puppies were about 10 weeks
old and they were so cute.

44
00:01:43,490 --> 00:01:45,120
They were play fighting with each other

45
00:01:45,120 --> 00:01:47,400
and yipping and barking.

46
00:01:47,400 --> 00:01:48,820
Some were black and white,

47
00:01:48,820 --> 00:01:50,330
some were brown and white,

48
00:01:50,330 --> 00:01:52,570
and one was completely black.

49
00:01:52,570 --> 00:01:54,950
My sister wanted the smallest one,

50
00:01:54,950 --> 00:01:57,700
a small brown and white puppy
who was sitting in the corner,

51
00:01:57,700 --> 00:02:00,120
far from the rest of the litter.

52
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:02,090
He looked scared and lonely.

53
00:02:02,090 --> 00:02:03,250
I wanted the black puppy,

54
00:02:03,250 --> 00:02:05,380
who was the biggest and most aggressive,

55
00:02:05,380 --> 00:02:08,830
just fighting with all of
its brothers and sisters.

56
00:02:08,830 --> 00:02:11,940
For some reason, my mom and
dad agreed with my sister

57
00:02:11,940 --> 00:02:13,230
and a few moments later,

58
00:02:13,230 --> 00:02:15,120
we were riding home in the car

59
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:17,790
with the small brown and
white scared little puppy,

60
00:02:17,790 --> 00:02:19,463
sitting on my sister's lap.

61
00:02:20,640 --> 00:02:22,870
When we got home, we
put the dog in the box

62
00:02:22,870 --> 00:02:25,610
and my sister played with
it for the next few hours.

63
00:02:25,610 --> 00:02:28,160
She loved the dog from
the moment she saw it.

64
00:02:28,160 --> 00:02:31,860
And it was clear that the
dog liked her a lot too.

65
00:02:31,860 --> 00:02:33,000
At the dinner table that night,

66
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:34,610
we talked about names for the dog.

67
00:02:34,610 --> 00:02:37,860
I suggested Brutus, as I
thought it sounded like a cool,

68
00:02:37,860 --> 00:02:39,070
tough name.

69
00:02:39,070 --> 00:02:40,990
My sister liked the name King,

70
00:02:40,990 --> 00:02:43,240
because our older dog was named Prince.

71
00:02:43,240 --> 00:02:45,000
My parents said that we could decide.

72
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:46,080
I liked her idea.

73
00:02:46,080 --> 00:02:48,760
And so we named the dog King.

74
00:02:48,760 --> 00:02:52,140
King grew quickly and soon
learned to do all the same things

75
00:02:52,140 --> 00:02:53,210
that Prince did.

76
00:02:53,210 --> 00:02:54,720
He helped to bring in the cows at night.

77
00:02:54,720 --> 00:02:57,130
He barked when strangers came to the farm.

78
00:02:57,130 --> 00:02:58,340
He chased cats a lot.

79
00:02:58,340 --> 00:03:00,740
Although, that wasn't
really one of his jobs,

80
00:03:00,740 --> 00:03:03,000
but he sure seemed to like it.

81
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:05,560
King lived a long and
happy life on the farm.

82
00:03:05,560 --> 00:03:06,990
And it became clear over the years,

83
00:03:06,990 --> 00:03:09,380
that King was my sister's dog.

84
00:03:09,380 --> 00:03:13,250
As you probably know, dogs
usually only have one real owner,

85
00:03:13,250 --> 00:03:16,000
even if they live with a
whole family of humans.

86
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:18,500
And he seemed to have chosen my sister.

87
00:03:18,500 --> 00:03:19,690
I was good with that.

88
00:03:19,690 --> 00:03:21,624
I'm not really a dog person anyways.

89
00:03:21,624 --> 00:03:25,124
